\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf4 \cb5 Summary: citation chaser is an R package ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/nealhaddaway/citationchaser"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 \ul \ulc6 https://github.com/nealhaddaway/citationchaser}}) which functions to automate this process by making use of the Lens.org API. An input article list can be used to return a list of all referenced records, and/or all citing records in the Lens.org database (consisting of PubMed, PubMed Central, CrossRef, Microsoft Academic Graph and CORE; '{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.lens.org/"}}{\fldrslt \cf6 \ul \ulc6 https://www.lens.org}}').\cb1 \
