\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf4 \cb5 Summary: An R package for frequentist meta-analysis A comprehensive set of functions providing frequentist methods for network meta-analysis: frequentist network meta-analysis; net heat plot and design-based decomposition of Cochran's Q; measures characterizing the flow of evidence between two treatments; ranking of treatments based on frequentist analogue of SUCRA; partial order of treatment rankings ('poset') and Hasse diagram for 'poset'; split direct and indirect evidence to check consistency; league table with network meta-analysis results; additive network meta-analysis for combinations of treatments; network meta-analysis of binary data using the Mantel-Haenszel method or the non-central hypergeometric distribution; 'comparison-adjusted' funnel plot; automated drawing of network graphs; rankograms and ranking by Surface Under the Cumulative RAnking curve (SUCRA) values; contribution matrix.\cb1 \
